 /medium/public/2025-12/generic_Arts_and_Music.png?itok=Bv9cGw69
DESCRIPTION:Teens\, join Jess Graff and create colorful paintings of vinta
 ge glassware and summer flowers. Learn basic techniques for capturing ligh
 t\, mixing color\, and mapping out unique artwork. All skill levels welcom
 e.Space is limited! Registration preferred\, but not required. Registratio
